{"tid":1714703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［德國示威］好多留言覺得道理去咗個大陸女人到！","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:48:17.000Z","uid":16032,"like":21,"dislike":174,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"57216f7ce3010751ad5b08834bebc479d430cc4e","tid":1714703,"uid":16032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:31:23.000Z","msg":"唔知起咩標題好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國港人示威有大陸女人行埋去講佢啲濕鳩理論<br />\n重點係班外國手足無乜理佢，無乜反駁佢，剩係繼續唱歌同嗌口號<br />\n仲話我地利用細路抗爭<br />\n然後言論風向，有七成留言變咗支持個大陸女人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x_SqKY5haqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx_SqKY5haqg&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE9wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=549e43c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x_SqKY5haqg</a><br />\n<br />\n我明大家對住呢啲大陸臭雞係會駁都廢撚事駁佢<br />\n明你地只係想瘋狂䎵笑佢<br />\n我知好難頂<br />\n但咁樣會令到其他人覺得道理係晒佢到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔割！！！<br />\n不完美，下次可以做好啲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bdf5f20e052872d438cc71ffe08ca8111f3450","tid":1714703,"uid":42629,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"D comment全部5毛黎<br />\n唔使理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a5fa708dda4ec1766dbc836d661237676d1f1d","tid":1714703,"uid":149978,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"中共：有隻蚊飛過"},{"pid":"861a83705e0a923f6422ff9bb26fa604ac620d0a","tid":1714703,"uid":10219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad9e3a69e1297553ed9d3c56d4f675dc8f1e2ab7","tid":1714703,"uid":46822,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":2